high_descs: Turn left and go toward the fridge, then turn left to go to the sink.
Pick up the egg in the right sink basin.
Turn around and go to the wall, then turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the egg inside and chill it, then take it out.
Turn around and step forward, then turn right to go to the sink.
Put the egg in the left sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold egg in the left sink basin.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the front of the sink.
Pick up the egg in the right sink.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the egg in the refrigerator and remove it.
Turn left and go back to the sink.
Place the egg in the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled egg in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up the egg in the right basin of the sink.
Turn around and veer left to the fridge.
Place the egg in the fridge, to the right of the rightmost glass. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn left and walk back to the sink.
Place the egg in the left sink, in front and to the left of the other egg.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled egg in a sink.
